Module org.example.proyecto
Package org.example.proyecto.gui

Class ApartmentListController

java.lang.Object
org.example.proyecto.gui.ApartmentListController
public class ApartmentListController extends Object
Controller class for managing the tourist apartment list in the GUI. Provides functionalities to register, update, delete, and search for apartments. Handles selection of apartments for booking.

  • Method Details

    • initialize

      public void initialize() throws SQLException, IOException
      Initializes the controller class. Sets up the table columns and loads the apartment data. Adds a listener to handle selection changes in the apartment table.
      Throws:
      SQLException - if a database access error occurs.
      IOException - if an input/output error occurs.

    • registerApartment

      public void registerApartment()
      Registers a new apartment with the data provided in the text fields. Validates the input data and shows alerts in case of missing information.

    • updateApartment

      public void updateApartment()
      Updates the selected apartment with the data provided in the text fields. Validates the input data and shows alerts in case of missing information or no changes.

    • deleteApartment

      public void deleteApartment()
      Deletes the selected apartment from the database. Shows an alert if no apartment is selected.

    • searchApartment

      public void searchApartment() throws SQLException, IOException
      Searches for apartments based on the data provided in the text fields. Displays the matching results in the apartment table.
      Throws:
      SQLException - if a database access error occurs.
      IOException - if an input/output error occurs.

    • selectApartmentForBooking

      public void selectApartmentForBooking()
      Selects the currently selected apartment for booking. Initializes the booking data and loads the booking list view. Shows an alert if no apartment is selected.

    • setTemplateComponent

      public void setTemplateComponent(javafx.scene.layout.AnchorPane templateComponent)
      Sets the template component.
      Parameters:
      templateComponent - the template component to set.

    • setIsSelectingHousing

      public void setIsSelectingHousing(boolean isSelectingApartment)
      Sets the visibility of the housing selection button.
      Parameters:
      isSelectingApartment - true to make the button visible, false to hide it.

    • setDataForBooking

      public void setDataForBooking(BookingDataHelper dataForBooking)

      Parameters:
      dataForBooking - the booking data helper to set.
